Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Docker containers fail to start

Check available memory: free -h (need at least 4GB free)
Verify Docker service: sudo systemctl status docker
Check logs: docker-compose logs [service_name]
Issue: Elasticsearch connection refused

Wait 60-90 seconds for Elasticsearch to fully initialize
Verify service is running: curl http://localhost:9200
Check container logs: docker logs so-elasticsearch
Issue: No data appearing in Kibana

Verify Logstash is processing logs: docker logs so-logstash
Check if indices exist: curl http://localhost:9200/_cat/indices
Ensure test events were generated: cat /var/log/auth.log | grep Failed
Issue: Python scripts fail with import errors

Install missing packages: pip3 install elasticsearch requests pandas matplotlib
Verify Python version: python3 --version (need 3.6+)
